  "body": "Error messages are not sufficiency descriptive when starting applications (eg. `op-node`). They should provide more information (possibly entire error stack) to the user in order for them to be able to pinpoint issue. \r\n\r\nIn the below example there is log output of `op-node` app, please note that this log output does not have enough description for user to understand issue without digging deep into source code.\r\n```\r\nt=2023-08-11T13:32:41+0000 lvl=eror msg=\"Unable to create the rollup node\"      error=\"401 Unauthorized: user project is inactive\\n\"\r\nt=2023-08-11T13:32:41+0000 lvl=crit msg=\"Application failed\"                    message=\"401 Unauthorized: user project is inactive\\n\"\r\n```",
